creator: Universiti Malaysia Sarawak
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the UNIMAS Now previously known as UNIMAS On The Go, the university's official mobile app!

Whether you are a student, staff or a member of the public, we are glad and excited to welcome you to experience our latest innovation.

Via this application, you will be notified about all the latest events and announcements in Universiti Malaysia Sarawak (UNIMAS) instantly and directly the same way you would receive your messaging/Whatsapp messages. If you are job seeker or a vendor looking for business opportunity in UNIMAS, you will not find any easier or faster way to get notified about latest job opening or business chances in UNIMAS.

Add any event directly to your phone calendar thus enabling you to plan your schedule more effectively. You even could enable alarm reminder for it and you will never forget and miss any important event anymore!

You could also share any events information with your friends by sharing it to your favorite apps such as Twitter, Facebook, Whatsapp, Line or any messaging apps including your trusted email and SMS.

This app is developed by Open Source Initiative and Advanced Technology Unit (OpSO), Centre for Information and Communication Technology Services (CICTS), Universiti Malaysia Sarawak.

***This application is only compatible with Android version 4.1.2 and above.

DISCLAIMER : The application has been developed and tested to the best of our efforts. However, we shall not be liable for any loss or damage caused by the usage of this application.
descriptionShort: Discover Universiti Malaysia Sarawak(UNIMAS) event & announcement in a new way!
